# .graphifyignore — files to exclude from the graphify corpus.
# Format: gitignore-style. Graphify does NOT read .gitignore, so rules
# here are independent of the project .gitignore.
#
# Graphify already auto-skips by default:
#   - Dirs: .git, node_modules, __pycache__, dist, build, graphify-out, env, ...
#   - Sensitive: *.env*, *.pem, *.key, anything matching
#     \b(credential|secret|passwd|password|token|private_key)s?\b

# Notepad++ editor backups. The env/nppBackup/ tree is already covered
# because env/ is in graphify's default SKIP_DIRS; this rule catches
# cliscripts-templates/nppBackup/ and is also defensive for any future
# .bak files at other paths.
nppBackup/
*.bak

# Graphify's own temp files and output directory. graphify-out/ is
# already in default SKIP_DIRS but listing it here keeps intent explicit.
.graphify*
graphify-out/

# Real Solace product license key. The substring "product key" does not
# match graphify's built-in sensitive-name regex, so explicit exclusion
# is required.
product key.txt

# Upstream Solace reference docs (~5000 lines combined). Useful for
# humans but not part of THIS repo's authored content, and they swamp
# the graph if included.
EventBrokerOperatorParametersReference.md
EventBrokerOperatorUserGuide.md

# Pre-rendered HTML duplicate of howto-deploy-solace.md. Including both
# would create double concept nodes from the same source content.
howto-deploy-solace.html

LICENSE

solace-theme-reference.md
.broker.yaml